<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>부산아이티 솔루션</title>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
                background-color: #f9f9f9;
            }
            .container {
                width: 100%;
                height: 90vh;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .main {
                max-width: 800px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            button {
                border: 0;
                padding: 18px 30px;
                border-radius: 50px;
                font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
                cursor: pointer;
            }
            button.left {
                background-color: #37b09b;
                color: white;
            }
            button.right {
                background-color: #e8edef;
                color: #37b09b;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 50px;
                line-height: 80px;
            }
            h4 {
                font-size: 30px;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="main">
                <h4>부산아이티 아카데미</h4>
                <h1>부산아카데미 그룹웨어 솔루션<br />그룹웨어 프로</h1>
                <a href="/userList"><button class="left">회원 관리 프로그램</button></a>
                <a href="/board"><button class="right">게시판 관리 프로그램</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
